2 MB Chip
120MB Conner 2 1/2" internal IDE HD
DataFlyer SCSI+ 1200 Scsi interface
Sony CDU-590 Double Speed SCSI CD-ROM
Hayes Accura 288 V.FC + FAX
Hewlett Packard DeskJet 540c
